Used Playwright as a UI automation framework (https://playwright.dev/docs/intro)

# Instructions

Please run `npm i` before running the test suite

# Run tests

`npm run test:headless` Runs the end-to-end tests.
`npm run test:ui`: Starts the interactive UI mode.
`npm run test:report` opens test report in a browser

# You can configure browsers in playwright.config.js

